org.hibernate.ogm.id.impl

Class OgmGeneratorBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.id.impl.OgmGeneratorBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, IdentifierGenerator, PersistentNoSqlIdentifierGenerator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OgmSequenceGenerator, OgmTableGenerator

    public abstract class OgmGeneratorBase
extends Object
implements PersistentNoSqlIdentifierGenerator, Configurable
    Base class for sequence and table based id generators in Hibernate OGM.

    Inspired by the corresponding classes in ORM (e.g. TableGenerator).

    Author:
    Steve Ebersole, Emmanuel Bernard <emmanuel@hibernate.org>, Gunnar Morling
